This was my second time here. My first time i ate in. It was a little slow but the food and service were pretty good. This time i carried out. When i got there i waited over 30 minutes for my food even though it was ordered 20 minutes prior to me getting there. I observed the cashier being rude again.  The back staff although nice was unorganized which i think accounted for the long wait. The seem to keep forgetting orders. I clearly wasnt the only customer waiting for a while which was confusing because food was constantly coming up. There was also a concern that none of the kitchen staff wore gloves. I saw cooks wipe their brow or head several times and it didnt look like they washed their hands but because of the counter i couldnt be sure. The only reason i gave 3 stars is because the food was still ok. It wasn't as good as my first experience. But it was still good. Also i didnt qualify for the special price by ordering online. I paid 22.99 for a crab and shrimp combo when is was priced at 15.99 in store. You cant order over the phone is what I was told. Only online or instore. Overall i was disappointed and felt i could have saved $40
